In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla and KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using lightly buttered spatula, press into buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9-inch) pan. Cut into six rectangles. To make remote controls, decorate with fruit chews for buttons. Attach chews with decorating gel and write numbers on them if desired.